high_descs: Turn and go to the toilet.
Grab the spray bottle that is on the back of the toilet on the left side.
Turn to your right and go to the metal shelf.
Place the spray bottle on the top shelf.
Turn around and go to the toilet.
Grab the spray bottle that is on the back of the toilet.
Turn to your right and go back to the metal shelf.
Place the spray bottle on the top shelf to the right of the one that is there.
Turn to your left and move to the front of the toilet.
Pick up the blue and white spray bottle from the left side of the toilet.
Turn around and cross the room to the metal rack in the corner left of the sink.
Put the spray bottle on the top shelf of the rack, pointing right.
Turn to your right and return to the toilet.
Get the remaining blue and white spray bottle from the back of the toilet.
Turn to your right, then return to the metal rack in the corner left of the sink.
Place the spray bottle to the immediate right of the first bottle, pointing the same direction.
anns.task_desc: Move two spray bottles from the toilet to a metal rack.

high_descs: Turn around to your left and go to the toilet.
Pick up the blue spray bottle that is closer to the flush handle of the toilet.
Turn around to your right and go to the metal shelves that are to the left of the sink.
Place the blue spray bottle on the top shelf of the metal shelving unit, to the right of the soap.
Turn around to your right and return to the toilet.
Pick up the blue spray bottle on top of the toilet, near the right-hand side.
Turn around to your right and go to the metal shelves that are to the left of the sink.
Place the blue spray bottle on the top shelf of the metal shelving unit, to the right of the other spray bottle.
anns.task_desc: Move both blue spray bottles to the top of the metal shelves.
